name: Enchanted Apple
description: Are you tired of the monotony of the everyday grind? Has life left you feeling drained and hopeless? Well, we can help you at the Teia Cafe. Our Enchanted Apple may be just what the doctor ordered. It's a blessing and a curse, in one delicious package. It has the power to grant you your deepest desire. With a minimal price to pay, your darkest fear will manifest simultaneously. What could possibly go wrong? We guarantee it will break the chains of despair and bring excitement back into your life.
